RENOIR loads dmub fw not dmcu, check dmcu only will prevent loading iram,
it breaks backlight control.

Bug: https://bugzilla.kernel.org/show_bug.cgi?id=208277
Signed-off-by: Aaron Ma <aaron.ma@canonical.com>
